snippet.title: Desperados III - Money for the Vultures Part 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Desperados III - Money for the Vultures Part 3: Once More With Feeling is OUT NOW.

In the epic finale of the 'Money for the Vultures' adventure, the gang travels to the famous Desperados fan favorite location: The 'Eagles Nest' bandit fortress. To impress Rosie, Hector has hatched an incredible plan, crazy enough that it just might work.
